    <div class="repair-grid">
      <div class="repair-card">
        <h3>Hestan GROR36 36-inch range, Calabasas</h3>
        <p><strong>Symptom:</strong> Quiet hum at convection start-up that owner had noticed for about 6 weeks, now becoming a clear grinding noise across the full bake cycle. Unit was 5 years old, 2020 GROR cohort.</p>
        <p><strong>Diagnosis:</strong> Classic 2018-2021 GROR convection fan bearing wear pattern. Fan bearing fully failed; motor running but with audible mechanical degradation. Other oven components within spec.</p>
        <p><strong>Repair:</strong> Convection fan motor replacement with OEM Hestan part (GROR motor in stock on truck). Verified clean convection cycle and even bake temperature.</p>
